---
title: Candidate Self-Registration — Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant MS as Merkle Service
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant SE as Sync Engine
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    S->>UI: Connect MetaMask & open portal
    UI->>API: GET /api/voters/me?wallet=0x...
    API-->>UI: Identity fields (name, year, gender)
    
    S->>UI: Click "Register as Candidate"
    UI->>API: GET /api/voters/identity-proof?wallet=0x...
    API->>MS: Generate identity Merkle proof
    MS-->>API: Proof array
    API-->>UI: { proof, identity }
    
    S->>UI: Select position (President/Secretary/GM)
    S->>UI: Upload profile photo
    UI->>API: POST /api/candidates/upload-photo
    API-->>UI: imageCID
    
    S->>UI: Submit registration
    UI->>SC: registerCandidate(guid, name, year, isFemale, imageCID, pos, proof)
    SC->>SC: Verify identity Merkle proof
    SC->>SC: Check position eligibility (year req)
    SC-->>UI: CandidateRegistered event
    
    SE->>SC: Poll for new candidate events
    SC-->>SE: Candidate struct
    SE->>DB: UPSERT candidates table
    SE-->>UI: Socket.IO blockchainEvent
    
    UI-->>S: "Registration confirmed! ID: 1"
